          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"key-insights\">Key Insights</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Turkey's tertiary enrollment surged from 12% to 128%, the most dramatic expansion in the dataset</li>\n<li>South Korea crossed 100% enrollment, meaning more students than the traditional college-age population</li>\n<li>China went from 3% to 77%, enrolling tens of millions of new university students</li>\n<li>Ethiopia remains below 10%, highlighting the persistent higher-education gap in Sub-Saharan Africa</li>\n</ul></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
